上超多..但我都是在B站上听的..没去别的地方找..前不久B站音声区大清洗 我收藏夹里居然掉了4个<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/05.gif\" smileid=\"44\" alt=\"(bgm28)\">(自认自己收藏的都是正常视频)<br>B站PPOMO搬运认准锦衣缇骑, 蓝月和浅见认准kami桃..都是超良心UP主..T7还会时不时推国内的ASMR实况主..<br>另外德叔有个<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av13916286\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">20小时超长ASMR</a>..可以一口气听个爽..<br><br>其实我的体质不适合听ASMR..听了几十分钟后直接免疫ASMR效果..一切ASMR都变得毫无感觉..哪怕原先多有感觉都没用<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/51.gif\" smileid=\"90\" alt=\"(bgm74)\">..只能花好几天等CD冷却了再听..导致其实自己听得不多<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/59/245983.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1378555","time":"2018-9-3 15:05","userId":"poker","userName":"Pokr","userSign":"","message":"啊 感谢司机指路<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/03.gif\" smileid=\"42\" alt=\"(bgm26)\">（咦为什么是司机）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/61/426156.jpg","floor":"#8-2","id":"1378558","time":"2018-9-3 15:35","userId":"426156","userName":"御坂的眼睛不说话","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Poker</span> 说: 啊 感谢司机指路（咦为什么是司机）</q></div>因为都在飙车"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/21/222174.jpg","floor":"#8-3","id":"1378560","time":"2018-9-3 15:55","userId":"vivids","userName":"为了道德","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Poker</span> 说: 啊 感谢司机指路（咦为什么是司机）</q></div>声音卖yin，颅内高潮"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#8-4","id":"1378637","time":"2018-9-3 22:57","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Poker</span> 说: 啊 感谢司机指路（咦为什么是司机）</q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">听得挺少的 收藏夹里都不够30个..<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">其实不太喜欢听18x的 一直觉得一个妹子一边啊啊啊一边亲口描述自己的遭遇超级奇怪b38<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">大概是老了</span></span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/